\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 AI-Assisted Trading Intelligence System\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 Purpose\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Build a personal AI-assisted trading intelligence system that helps identify medium- and short-term stock opportunities through a combination of financial analysis, market data, technical signals, and AI-driven research synthesis.\
The goal is not to build an automated trading bot or a high-frequency trading system. Instead, the goal is to build a decision-support system that continuously monitors a curated set of stocks, analyzes them using a structured framework, and surfaces actionable insights and opportunities in a consistent, data-driven manner.\
The system is being built for a single user with a strong technical and product background, but without formal institutional investing infrastructure or deep professional trading expertise. Today, much of the analysis required to make informed trading decisions is fragmented across earnings calls, news articles, charts, analyst commentary, SEC filings, and financial dashboards. Synthesizing all of this manually is time-consuming, inconsistent, and difficult to scale across dozens of stocks simultaneously.\
As a result:\
