\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Research quality varies week to week\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 There is no systematic way to validate whether a strategy is actually working over time\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 The objective of this project is to create a structured, repeatable, AI-assisted investing workflow that combines both long-term company analysis and short-term trading opportunity detection.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
